narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Elementary Korean. Core vocabulary, expressions, spelling, grammar etc.
I developed some basic knowledge of Hangeul and Korean grammar/sentence structure. I also learned about Korean culture.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course was excellent! Ample time was given to reinforcing the core concepts learned through the course, to ensure that nothing was forgotten.
The class was very engaging and I always felt like the information we were learning was understandable. At times the pacing of the class could have been improved.
went very quickly through learning korean, which is both a strength and a weakness

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. The teaching was excellent. The course is well designed and takes into account a variety of different learning styles.
I would recommend this course to any student looking to learn Korean.
yes, anyone interested in learning korean and about korean culture should take this class
